Noah Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noah_Taylor 0 Noah George Taylor (born 4 September 1969) is an English-Australian actor. He is best known for his roles as teenage David Helfgott in Shine, Locke in HBO series Game of Thrones, Mr. Bucket in Charlie and the Chocolate Factory and Danny in the Australian cult film He Died with a Felafel in His Hand. Taylor also starred as Adolf Hitler in Max and Preacher. Noah_George_Taylor ( born 4_September_1969 ) is an_English-Australian_actor .
